### Scenarios Include  

- **Overfished**: emulates a groundfish stock in poor status (Gulf of Maine cod) <br>

- **Not Overfished**: emulates a groundfish stock in good status with large recruitment event (Geroges Bank Haddock) <br>

- **Mortality Misspecified**: natural mortality misspecification in stock assessment <br>

- **Recruitment Misspecified**: recruitment misspecification in stock assessment <br>

- **Catchability Misspecified**: survey catchability misspecification in stock assessment <br>

- **Rho-adjusted**: <br>

- **Not rho-adjusted**: <br>
